OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776731804
OL,3,CTsunami warning after powerful 7.5-
OL,4,Cmagnitude earthquake strikes off Japan
OL,6,FTsunami alerts have been issued after
OL,7,Fa powerful earthquake struck off the
OL,8,Fcoast of Japan.
OL,10,FThe quake off the coast of Sanriku in
OL,11,Fnorthern Japan registered a
OL,12,Fpreliminary magnitude of 7.5 at around
OL,13,F4:53 p.m. (0753 GMT), at a depth of
OL,14,Fabout 10 kilometres (6 miles) below
OL,15,Fthe sea surface, the Japan
OL,16,FMeteorological Agency said. The US
OL,17,FTsunami Warning System has reported
OL,18,Fthe quake as 7.4 magnitude.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
