CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776731804
OL,3,CTsunami warning after powerful 7.5-
OL,4,Cmagnitude earthquake strikes off Japan
OL,6,FA tsunami of about 80 centimetres (2.6
OL,7,Ffeet) was detected at the Kuji port in
OL,8,Fthe Iwate prefecture, and a smaller
OL,9,Ftsunami of 40 centimetres (1.3 feet)
OL,10,Fwas recorded at another port in the
OL,11,Fprefecture, the Japan Meteorological
OL,12,FAgency said. There have been warnings
OL,13,Fof waves of up to 3 metres (10 feet)
OL,14,Fissued.
OL,16,FJapan's prime minister Sanae Takaichi
OL,17,Furged people to seek safety on higher
OL,18,Fground.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
