PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776731804
OL,3,CTsunami warning after powerful 7.5-
OL,4,Cmagnitude earthquake strikes off Japan
OL,6,FShe told reporters authorities were
OL,7,Fdoing their "utmost to assess the
OL,8,Fdamage, implement emergency disaster
OL,9,Fresponse measures such as search and
OL,10,Frescue operations, and provide timely
OL,11,Fand accurate information to the
OL,12,Fpublic."
OL,14,FTakaichi added: "At this time, we are
OL,15,Fstill confirming the extent of human
OL,16,Fand material damage, but we will
OL,17,Freceive detailed reports shortly and
OL,18,Fproceed with disaster response
OL,19,Fefforts."
