OL,3,CTsunami warning after powerful 7.5-
OL,4,Cmagnitude earthquake strikes off Japan
OL,6,FA magnitude 9.0 earthquake and tsunami
OL,7,Fstruck northern Japan on March 11,
OL,8,F2011, causing more than 22,000 deaths
OL,9,Fand forcing nearly half a million
OL,10,Fpeople to flee their homes, most of
OL,11,Fthem due to tsunami damage.
OL,13,FThe Fukushima Daiichi nuclear power
OL,14,Fplant was damaged by the tsunami,
OL,15,Fforcing tens of thousands to evacuate
OL,16,Ftheir homes due to radiation concerns.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
